item.title: ::Mypos
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Sorry for the delay, got sidetracked.

So here’s what I believe your issue is.
Both of your mypos commands are in the administratorCommands method.
And you are probably an owner.
Well, you haven’t made it so owners can do admin commands. See this:

[code=java] if (c.playerRights == 2)
administratorCommands(c, playerCommand);

	if (c.playerRights == 3 || c.playerRights == 6 || c.isOwner())
		ownerCommands(c, playerCommand);[/code]

Only players with the rights of 2 can do admin commands, no one else. May want to make an exception for owners.
